data.description: Custom built estate property at an affordable price in the heart of Daphne located in Avalon Subdivision.  This home is underpriced to allow for the future owner to renovate and restore to their taste.  This private lot backs up to peaceful farmland with unobstructed views.  This 4 bedroom 3 and a half bath with a huge bonus room upstairs, and an office downstairs, has 3 bedrooms down and 1 up.  The home features a split plan with the primary bedroom and private attached bath located across the living room from the other bedrooms.  This custom constructed home has a separate dining room, breakfast room, high ceilings with upgraded moldings, hardwood floors in the living areas with carpet in the bedrooms and bonus room.  The chef's kitchen has loads of storage, a pantry, custom cabinetry, gas range and granite counter tops.  There are multiple fireplaces in this home.  Inside in the living room is a beautiful gas fireplace which accents the cozy warm feeling of the interior.  Outside are two additional woodburning fireplaces, and a sunroom off of the living room that's accessible from the primary bedroom and breakfast room.  The sunroom leads to the screen enclosed outdoor pool and large fenced in private back yard.  There is also a 3 car garage with storage.  With a little work this home could be a real showcase property.  The established neighborhood has sidewalks, a lake stocked with fish, and a community pier for the residents.  This sought after community boasts only custom homes with larger estate sized lots.  Easy to view.
